      "content": "but it's not just \"tough periods.\" it's everything. i've tried the therapy, the meds, the new jobs... it's like there's this fundamental glitch in me. no matter what i do, i end up right back where i started, just more broken than before. it feels like the universe is literally designed to keep me in this loop.",
