      "content": "i've seen the specialists. i've done the \"professional\" stuff. it doesn't change the fact that the result is always the same. it's like i'm stuck in a script that's already been written. no matter how many times i try to deviate, the loop just pulls me back in. it feels so pointless to keep fighting a script that can't be changed.",
